summary: An Ordinance accepting deed from F. J. Kwapil and Mamie Kwapil, his wife; Silas Archibald and Elizabeth J., his wife; Mathew Cashman and Anna Cashman, his wife; Thomas K. Clarke and Sarah D. Clarke, his wife, to the City of Seattle, to a certain portion of Blocks 30 and 42, Mercer's 2nd Addition to the City of Seattle.
